title: Patriots-Giants TNF Recap, New England defense does it again (Football 10/11)
description:
John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough recap the Patriots victory over the Giants, focusing on another stellar effort from New England's defense, a mediocre performance from Tom Brady and New York sticking around longer than expected. The guys also evaluate the outlook for each team the rest of the season.
